c) Evaluate the nature of the transactions and account the revenue transactions in the period to which they relate to.

d) Ensure that all revenues recognized are with legal basis and are fully supported with contracts, MOA and other pertinent documents.

We recommended that the Municipal Mayor to:

a) Direct the above-mentioned key officials to accomplish the duties and responsibilities assigned to them;

